Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(名字是?)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.30,0:00:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好,我是冲田杏梨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.37,0:00:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(听说今天的内容了吗?)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基本上有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.65,0:00:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(请说）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要男女同时高潮才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(过去有同时的经验吗？)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍片的话只有几次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(那时会如何?)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽感会不同,比平时更高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.02,0:01:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(这回请绝对要在最后同时高潮)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.23,0:01:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后而已吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.56,0:01:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(最后而已)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中途不行是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(中途不可以各自高潮)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊？那很困扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦了,我的体质是很容易去的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.92,0:01:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前是中途也会\N但只有最后的是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.59,0:01:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(之前有忍耐过吗?)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没在拍片中忍过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(同时高潮升天的SEX)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么才容易去？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶头很敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么用呢?…摸啦,咬啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其它呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这好赞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍得住吗?…我忍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一件式的?…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从下面开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快一点的如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屁股也要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真下流的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不仃,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去了,不行,太激烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,内裤脱了来用了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出来点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好难受…跪趴好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屁股翘好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没去吧?.…没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己张开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦…别乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:16:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会一下就的哦.…不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,张大点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有冷静一点吗？那来互舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,膝盖起来,好好对着我的睑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要来插了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么强,会不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.57,0:21:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要多用点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.66,0:21:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要忍住…我努力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.73,0:21:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去了吗?…没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的没去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.68,0:22:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超湿的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.08,0:22:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好忍住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.77,0:22:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好有感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好好忍吗?…有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.23,0:23:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好深啊…难受吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.87,0:24:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 快去了...只是动就？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.48,0:24:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.27,0:25:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.05,0:25:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.73,0:26:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插得要不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.87,0:26:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.87,0:26:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么?…快不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.15,0:26:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,含一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.63,0:26:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己的穴汁什么味?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.90,0:26:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叉甜叉咸
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.19,0:27:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍得了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.73,0:27:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来翘好,手放下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.35,0:27:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,来罗 自己放进去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.32,0:28:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.59,0:28:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脚进来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.75,0:28:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 要去去…不行了?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.57,0:29:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.93,0:29:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对着我.…站着插吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.27,0:29:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插入了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.36,0:30:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.71,0:31:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多哦…不行了,忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.78,0:31:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要忍住啊…不行了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.17,0:32:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.65,0:32:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样插会不行
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.94,0:33:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍住了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.69,0:33:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再多来一点
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.24,0:33:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.11,0:33:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是好赞
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.19,0:33:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不行了…那好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.67,0:34:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.61,0:34:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去了…要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.10,0:35:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.44,0:35:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.04,0:35:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.25,0:35:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整个溃堤后,最后超爽
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.52,0:36:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(有同时高潮吗?)
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.53,0:36:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完美,不同时也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.20,0:36:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(身上都是精液哦)
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.67,0:36:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好赞,都是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.74,0:36:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(忍住不去很难受吗?)
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.28,0:36:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很难受啊,一直怕忍不住
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.49,0:36:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐真的不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.02,0:36:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(真的有确实没去吗?)
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.29,0:36:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是有,有好好用到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.84,0:36:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(和忍耐时不同吗?)
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.77,0:37:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感度完全不同,很赞
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.76,0:37:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.63,0:37:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很赞的样子在等呢\N是被要求这个样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.64,0:38:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.11,0:38:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.38,0:38:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反应好赞呢,我很担心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.59,0:38:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没同时,就算只有一点也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.61,0:38:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被用就会很快射啊...不行
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.75,0:38:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要同时才行,能答应我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.49,0:38:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会的…能答应我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.10,0:39:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能吗?.…我行的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.30,0:39:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶头很有活力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.05,0:39:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会同时的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.32,0:39:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不同时不会放你回去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.81,0:39:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摸了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.69,0:39:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前端不难受吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.16,0:40:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.56,0:40:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前端湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.17,0:40:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你摸啊\N摸就这样吗?…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.31,0:40:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能射哦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.47,0:40:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道会用什么吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.82,0:40:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.16,0:41:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老二顶到了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.58,0:41:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难受吗?…好赞
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.13,0:41:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.27,0:41:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就有点想射了...不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.35,0:42:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在舔奶头?…爽吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.96,0:42:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶头…怎么?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.69,0:42:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用得很好…是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.17,0:42:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好,那这么?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.37,0:42:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反应超大的…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.13,0:42:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要用什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.35,0:43:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不到比平时更兴奋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.31,0:43:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再快一点就会射的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.38,0:43:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就说再快会射的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.12,0:43:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,要射了…不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.73,0:44:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的一定要一起吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.80,0:44:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就说不同时不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.74,0:44:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是会想射了...不行,今天要等我
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.99,0:44:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊?…好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.53,0:45:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.80,0:45:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像小朋友一样吸
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.37,0:45:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在摩了…用着老二哦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.78,0:45:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会射的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.55,0:46:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会忍耐好的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.16,0:46:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何?…比较不会想射
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.30,0:46:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老二慢慢忍得住了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.90,0:46:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就给你用上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.18,0:47:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢忍得住了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.19,0:47:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这什么啊?…你觉得呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.26,0:47:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好软
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.89,0:47:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽…是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.77,0:47:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.50,0:48:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.12,0:48:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以休息一下吗?…流汁了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.99,0:48:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老二想休息了…想休息啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.86,0:48:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快射了啊…是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.33,0:48:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换我来吧\N你来吗?那像狗一样来舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.41,0:48:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来舔顶上的小穴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.22,0:48:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.98,0:49:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么下流地舔,好兴奋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.43,0:50:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抬起来舔哦,都用到了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.04,0:50:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.91,0:50:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好吸我的穴汁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.95,0:51:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.55,0:51:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,要一起
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.63,0:51:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要和老二出汁一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.03,0:51:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直用着小穴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.58,0:51:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.66,0:51:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.00,0:51:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来让我爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.14,0:51:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是好湿
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.41,0:52:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子会射的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.28,0:52:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用什么?.…膝盖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.29,0:52:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着就快射了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.29,0:52:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就会射了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.04,0:52:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用强一点
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.78,0:52:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.92,0:52:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗?…就那里
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.86,0:52:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样好爽,多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.66,0:52:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很容易去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.34,0:53:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流好多下流汁啊…你不也是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.48,0:53:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是流汁了...一起出来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.32,0:53:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起好难啊…是啊,好难
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.79,0:53:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那来插吧,用这湿湿的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.20,0:54:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.61,0:54:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.82,0:54:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子一起都好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.50,0:54:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好有感觉啊…再多感觉一点
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.39,0:54:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.02,0:55:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.63,0:55:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里头好湿好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.18,0:55:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以自己射哦
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.46,0:56:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.14,0:56:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,子宫在搅动着
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.68,0:56:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.75,0:56:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要好好忍住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.82,0:56:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.44,0:56:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要忍住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.18,0:57:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不能射哦
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.65,0:57:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还要更爽哦,来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.20,0:58:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真危险…快去了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.60,0:58:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是快去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.48,0:58:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽…不忍就会射的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.68,0:58:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被插得好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.70,0:59:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.91,0:59:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没完哦
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.21,0:59:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢动如何?…好赞
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.35,0:59:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好有感觉…有感觉被吸住吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.55,0:59:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好有感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.06,1:00:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插得好深啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.20,1:00:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直来呢
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.27,1:00:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样很容易射…是吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.91,1:01:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小穴好抖呢
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.98,1:01:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快要射了呢…是吗?还想要更多
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.92,1:01:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没好哦,快来
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.40,1:01:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对,那里,知道得很快嘛,进来了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.62,1:02:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好热啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.97,1:02:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么有喜欢吗?…我最爱被插了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.47,1:02:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么好色地用,会射的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.74,1:03:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不到会不行的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.41,1:03:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那拿掉罗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.55,1:03:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿掉了就再来一些吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.91,1:03:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋蛋也碰到了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.72,1:03:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直在抖呢…抖很大呢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.99,1:03:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.53,1:03:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.67,1:04:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓好时机一起高潮吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.95,1:04:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.11,1:04:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直插着呢
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.99,1:05:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好湿呢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.26,1:05:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深插好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.87,1:05:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.56,1:05:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摸奶头会射的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.96,1:05:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里？要我这么？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.83,1:05:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是好湿...要一起哦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.99,1:06:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了...快要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.60,1:06:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.28,1:06:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以射吗?…一起爽吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.50,1:06:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快要去了吗?\N是啊,阴核还很有活力
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.00,1:07:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以射了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.75,1:07:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.68,1:08:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时真是太赞了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.09,1:08:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射好多啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.50,1:09:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.10,1:09:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道今天做什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.18,1:09:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要-起高潮
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.66,1:09:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时好好享受
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.73,1:09:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.14,1:09:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后是要同时哦
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.14,1:09:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能有人先跑哦
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.96,1:10:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天不但要爽,还一起来互相自慰吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.38,1:10:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敏感吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.59,1:10:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好赞呢
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.53,1:10:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到这么赞
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.00,1:10:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很在意吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.87,1:10:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先来摸哦
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.09,1:11:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊…去搓老二吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.96,1:11:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左撇子吗?那换手…其实我都行
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.84,1:11:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶很大,要好好揉哦
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.04,1:11:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以2只手来吗？…可以啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.05,1:11:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好赞
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.58,1:11:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直很想摸吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.26,1:11:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶头出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.33,1:11:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.00,1:11:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛吗?...不会,有下流的爽感
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.80,1:11:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶头硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.28,1:12:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶头好有感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.81,1:12:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以搓老二吗?…可以
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.49,1:12:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搓着哦,好翘啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.76,1:12:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想舔吗?真的?…想要
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.10,1:12:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边搓老二边舔
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.59,1:12:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我看老二,起来
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.53,1:12:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好赞,内裤脱了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.07,1:13:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好赞.龟头好大
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.48,1:13:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来互相自慰吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.95,1:13:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,握好
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.76,1:13:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用给我看哦
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.90,1:13:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有下流吗?…好下流
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.52,1:13:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天来用玩具吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.20,1:14:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看啊,也好好用吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.87,1:14:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以近一点吗?...靠过来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.95,1:14:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这震度好强…是吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.15,1:14:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,内裤很贴身,震动很容易感受到
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.30,1:14:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.11,1:14:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好好看着吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.98,1:14:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看啊,陷进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.79,1:14:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用进去罗
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.34,1:15:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要强一点
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.21,1:15:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这震动好赞
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.29,1:15:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽,看到在动了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.49,1:15:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你搓起来
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.58,1:15:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用内裤了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.58,1:16:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我脱了…可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.33,1:16:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脱下来了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.81,1:16:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好赞
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.95,1:16:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好赞,看到了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.55,1:16:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有看清楚吗?...好清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.69,1:16:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了,来用吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.23,1:16:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以摸吗?…我用开吧…这样子?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.64,1:17:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好清楚,都看到了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.65,1:17:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阴核好爽啊…阴核?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.52,1:17:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是阴核
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.53,1:17:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了…有硬了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.40,1:17:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香啊…真的?…想舔吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.01,1:17:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来舔吧…真美…要吃得津津有味哦
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.70,1:17:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.37,1:18:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.31,1:18:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么认真真可爱…好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.26,1:18:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要边舔边搓哦
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.01,1:18:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.74,1:18:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.02,1:18:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好湿啊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.42,1:18:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办?快要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.16,1:18:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先去就结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.17,1:19:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去了…我也快不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.57,1:19:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,还没一起啊.头躺着
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.45,1:19:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠上去吧…这么?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.26,1:19:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来近近地看
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.54,1:19:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是美味的小穴哦
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.36,1:20:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗?…好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.43,1:20:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搓起来吧,好赞
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.97,1:20:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽,快射了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.18,1:20:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再一次.拜托了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.05,1:20:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很难受吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.86,1:20:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太赞了,再让我来一次
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.40,1:20:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那换边吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.07,1:20:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这么下去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.68,1:20:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再给你用哦…麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.68,1:21:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好赞
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.95,1:21:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要射时就停,不能射哦
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.24,1:21:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.71,1:21:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要温柔地舔哦.这么兴奋啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.79,1:21:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.42,1:22:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.63,1:22:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.57,1:22:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没一起哦,要好好舔
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.74,1:23:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能射哦
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.74,1:23:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直很有反应啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.35,1:23:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想去了,一起来用哦
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.22,1:23:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.63,1:23:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.76,1:23:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来更爽吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.57,1:23:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次用这个
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.31,1:23:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电马?…来一起高潮哦
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.65,1:23:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.73,1:24:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.41,1:24:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.08,1:24:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽吗?…好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.75,1:24:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是哦
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.17,1:24:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.77,1:24:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.38,1:24:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快不行了?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.05,1:24:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我快要了……就-起高潮吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.67,1:25:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好赞
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.81,1:25:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好,要不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.69,1:25:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要不行了…再来一点
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.37,1:25:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.71,1:25:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.92,1:26:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要射了,可以吗?射了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.83,1:26:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射好多,同时了呢,好湿啊
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.05,1:30:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好有感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.94,1:30:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来用吧…用出来
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.08,1:31:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想看吗?…想,用出来
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.69,1:31:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真主动啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.86,1:31:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好有感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.20,1:31:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.92,1:36:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.16,1:36:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.57,1:36:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会这么啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.44,1:36:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才好…不行,会太爽
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.65,1:37:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会太爽的
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.53,1:37:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.14,1:37:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多摇一点哦
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.15,1:37:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好有活力的老二
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.66,1:38:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这对奶夹老二太爽了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.40,1:38:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好湿啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.28,1:38:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面也要
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.23,1:40:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.98,1:40:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.92,1:40:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己的小穴味哦
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.39,1:40:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,味道真好
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.06,1:40:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好吗?…有下流味
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.23,1:42:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好湿了,想要插
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.32,1:42:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会射的
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.73,1:42:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会射的
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.44,1:43:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好赞,小穴好湿了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.68,1:44:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用力插啊
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.55,1:44:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.63,1:44:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不行
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.46,1:45:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么?…快不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.79,1:46:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.27,1:46:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.78,1:47:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快要去了,受不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.22,1:47:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.73,1:48:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.36,1:49:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么好色不行啦\N因为很想要老二啊
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.90,1:49:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.48,1:49:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去了?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.97,1:50:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去了,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.84,1:50:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小穴太容易去了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.87,1:50:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.44,1:51:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.45,1:51:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,子宫被顶得受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.80,1:51:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.54,1:53:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.60,1:54:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.01,1:54:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去了吗?…要去了,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.22,1:54:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:15.34,1:55:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:20.54,1:55:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子不行啦
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.53,1:56:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(今天一天如何?)
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.13,1:56:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天同时高潮真是新发现
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.87,1:56:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐最后再解放,有着10倍的爽感
Dialogue: 0,1:56:36.48,1:56:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(10倍吗?)
Dialogue: 0,1:56:39.15,1:56:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直推到爽点,最后就一片空白
Dialogue: 0,1:56:49.83,1:56:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太赞所以10倍不同呢
Dialogue: 0,1:56:53.84,1:57:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深处是很强的性感带
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.05,1:57:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是一直顶着又要忍,很辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.12,1:57:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(说了插到深处呢)
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.99,1:57:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太爽就会这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.13,1:57:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(途中咬了起来呢)
Dialogue: 0,1:57:22.66,1:57:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这里就有点
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.07,1:57:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为忍得太难受,所以想来有点痛觉
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.95,1:57:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(一起高潮有开心吗?)
Dialogue: 0,1:57:43.35,1:57:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果一直同时,感情会好呢
Dialogue: 0,1:57:51.89,1:57:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉得心理上也会不同

